Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.94,0:00:20.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.93,0:01:21.86,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur1}記憶之扉敞開的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.96,0:01:23.89,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur1}你想一同聆聽
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.95,0:01:28.10,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,400)\blur1}我便傾訴於你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.83,0:01:37.20,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}啊 雖然這般
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.27,0:01:40.79,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}重要的回憶也會
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.86,0:01:44.54,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}被時間之沙掩蓋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.60,0:01:48.80,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}而變得曖昧不明
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.83,0:01:55.45,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}說著「命運」這詞是如此廉價
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.54,0:01:59.82,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}而與我一同開懷大笑的你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.90,0:02:05.30,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}又是否是我生命中的羅密歐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.48,0:02:10.03,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}大家 一定會將自己的珍惜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.13,0:02:13.84,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}逐漸忘卻在心的角落
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.92,0:02:16.91,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}與你的一分一秒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.99,0:02:20.83,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}即使只有一瞬 也請留在心中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.99,0:02:24.29,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}即使成為無法集齊的拼圖
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.38,0:02:28.08,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}那無法尋覓的最後一片
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.15,0:02:31.17,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}記憶之扉敞開的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.23,0:02:33.17,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}你想一同聆聽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.28,0:02:39.50,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,600)\blur1}我便傾訴於你
